*sooperlooper-1.6.3 (28 Apr 2008)

  28 Apr 2008; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org>
  -files/sooperlooper-1.6.2-asneeded.patch,
  -files/sooperlooper-1.6.2-gcc43.patch, -sooperlooper-1.6.2.ebuild,
  +sooperlooper-1.6.3.ebuild:
  Version bump to patch free version, upstream applied both -Wl,--as-needed
  and GCC 4.3 fix.

  28 Apr 2008; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org>
  +files/sooperlooper-1.6.2-gcc43.patch, sooperlooper-1.6.2.ebuild:
  GCC 4.3 fix wrt #219542, thanks to Peter Alfredsen.

*sooperlooper-1.6.2 (27 Mar 2008)

  27 Mar 2008; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org>
  +files/sooperlooper-1.6.2-asneeded.patch, +sooperlooper-1.6.2.ebuild:
  Version bump wrt #212570, thanks to Arne Babenhauserheide for reporting.
  Upstream seems to have 1.6.3 also available, but they forgot to upload
  source package.

  27 Jul 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  +files/sooperlooper-1.1.0-asneeded.patch, sooperlooper-1.1.0.ebuild:
  fix build with asneeded, bug #186817

  27 Jul 2007; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org> sooperlooper-1.1.0.ebuild:
  Stop using upstream optimization flags and respect users. Install bundled
  documentation. Move epatch from src_compile to src_unpack.

  14 May 2007; Ryan Hill <dirtyepic@gentoo.org> -sooperlooper-1.0.8c.ebuild:
  Remove old.

  07 May 2007; Ryan Hill <dirtyepic@gentoo.org>
  +files/sooperlooper-1.1.0-amd64.patch, sooperlooper-1.0.8c.ebuild,
  sooperlooper-1.1.0.ebuild:
  Add patch for build failure on amd64 (bug #176751).

*sooperlooper-1.1.0 (30 Apr 2007)

  30 Apr 2007; Ryan Hill <dirtyepic@gentoo.org> -sooperlooper-1.0.3.ebuild,
  sooperlooper-1.0.8c.ebuild, +sooperlooper-1.1.0.ebuild:
  Version bump. Fix wxwidgets usage to work with upcoming changes. Remove
  ancient versions.

